OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start towards the east,
OL,6,Fotherwise another sunny, dry and hot
OL,7,Fday today. An easterly breeze however
OL,8,Fwill continue to strengthen especially
OL,9,Fover the hills, offering some relief
OL,10,Fto the heat later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining dry, warm but
OL,13,Fbreezy overnight with plenty of clear
OL,14,Fskies. Some patchy mist and low cloud
OL,15,Fhowever may develop later in the night
OL,16,Facross the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
