OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny overnight mist and low
OL,6,Fcloud quickly clearing to leave a dry
OL,7,Fand sunny but breezy day across Wales.
OL,8,FFeeling very warm once again as the
OL,9,Fheatwave continues.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FLittle
OL,12,Fchanges throughout the middle of the
OL,13,Fweek with the largely dry, settled and
OL,14,Fvery warm weather continuing. A small
OL,15,Fchance of a few thunderstorms
OL,16,Fdeveloping by Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
